        <div class="overline"><span class="overline__section">Perspective</span><span class="overline__subject">Psychology</span></div>
            <h1 class="article__headline"><div class="highwire-cite-title">How to overcome prejudice</div></h1>
              <div class="article byline byline--article"><div class="highwire-markup"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" id="content-block-markup" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><div xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="contributors"><ol class="contributor-list" id="contrib-group-1"><li class="last" id="contrib-1"><span class="name">Elizabeth Levy Paluck</span></li></ol><ol class="affiliation-list"><li class="aff"><a id="aff-1" name="aff-1"></a><address>Department of Psychology and Public and International Affairs, Princeton University, Princeton, NJ 08544, USA.</address></li></ol><ol class="corresp-list"><li class="corresp" id="corresp-1">E-mail: <span class="em-link"><span class="em-addr"><a href="mailto:epaluck@princeton.edu">epaluck@princeton.edu</a></span></span></li></ol></div></div></div></div>
      </header>

  <div class="meta-line">
    <cite>Science </cite> 08 Apr 2016:<br />Vol. 352, Issue 6282, pp. 147<br />DOI: 10.1126/science.aaf5207      </div>
</div>
<div id="hw-article-author-popups-node677188" style="display: none;"><div class="author-tooltip-0"><div class="author-tooltip-name"><span class="nlm-given-names">Elizabeth Levy</span> <span class="nlm-surname">Paluck</span> </div><div class="author-tooltip-affiliation"><span class="author-tooltip-text"><span class="nlm-aff">Department of Psychology and Public and International Affairs, Princeton University, Princeton, NJ 08544, USA.</span></span></div><ul class="author-tooltip-find-more"><li class="author-tooltip-gs-link first"><a href="/lookup/google-scholar?link_type=googlescholar&amp;gs_type=author&amp;author[0]=E.%20L.%2BPaluck" target="_blank" class="" data-icon-position="" data-hide-link-title="0">Find this author on Google Scholar</a></li>
<li class="author-tooltip-pubmed-link"><a href="/lookup/external-ref?access_num=Paluck%20EL&amp;link_type=AUTHORSEARCH" target="_blank" class="" data-icon-position="" data-hide-link-title="0">Find this author on PubMed</a></li>
<li class="author-site-search-link last"><a href="/search/author1%3AElizabeth%2BLevy%2BPaluck%2B" class="" data-icon-position="" data-hide-link-title="0">Search for this author on this site</a></li>
</ul></div></div></div>  </div>

  
