      <div class="highwire-cite-highlight media__icon"><a href="/content/352/6282" class="highlight-image-linked"><img class="highlight-image" src="https://d2ufo47lrtsv5s.cloudfront.net/sites/default/files/styles/sci_issue_archive_cover/public/highwire/sci/352/6282.cover-source.gif?itok=n_ShTryn" alt="Science: 352 (6282)" /></a></div>
