    <div class="media__body">
        <h3 class="highwire-cite-title-wrapper media__headline"><div class="highwire-cite-title media__headline__title">How to overcome prejudice</div></h3>
            <p class="highwire-cite-authors byline">By <span class="highwire-citation-authors"><span class="highwire-citation-author first" data-delta="0">Elizabeth Levy Paluck</span></span></p>
            <p class="highwire-cite-metadata byline"><em>Science</em><time>08 Apr 2016</time> : 147 </p>
                <div class="highwire-cite-snippet media__deck">
      <div class="highwire-markup"><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" class="section precis" id="abstract-1" xmlns:xhtml="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><p id="p-1">A brief conversation can have a lasting effect on prejudice <span class="named-content related-content" id="named-content-1">[Also see Report by <a href="/lookup/doi/10.1126/science.aad9713">Broockman and Kalla</a>]</span></p></div></div>    </div>
